leads.lead_text: Plants glabrous (or with scattered hairs) except for the calyx-tube; labellum with a subulate appendage and sensitive point at the cleft apex
Plants pubescent throughout; labellum without a subulate appendage and sensitive point
Leaves and stems usually reddish; labellum scarcely coloured and shorter than calyx-lobes; stigma entire
Leaves and stems green throughout; labellum deep purple and almost equal in length to calyx-lobes; stigma 2-lobed
